Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:42.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}是我無可替代的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:47.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,300)}溫柔的夢
